summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to incur an indebtedness against the general fund on account of the cost and expense of the improvement of Leary Avenue from 9th Avenue Northwest to Ione Place, in connection with the improvement of Shilshole Avenue et al, as provided for in Ordinance No. 30389, creating Local Improvement District No. 2601 and appropriating money therefor.
